content:
Apple has removed TikTok from the US App store;
Google has removed TikTok from the US Google Play. ​​​
TikTok pushed a shutdown notice to users on the evening of the 18th local time: Due to the US official ban taking effect on the 19th, the TikTok platform will temporarily stop serving users. The notice said that the company is working hard to resume services in the US as soon as possible and thanked users for their support of the platform.
